-- Ivory Coast Stampede Kills at Least 60 People, Official Says
-- B y   B a u d e l a i r e   M i e u
-- 2013-01-01T13:36:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-01/ivory-coast-stampede-kills-at-least-60-people-official-says.html
At least 60 people, including 26
children, died today in a stampede following a New Year’s Eve
fireworks display in Abidjan, Ivory Coast’s commercial capital,
an official at the civil protection office said.  The crush took place at 1 a.m. in Plateau, Abidjan’s
business district, where people had gathered to celebrate the
new  year, Fiacre Kili, general director of the civil protection
office said in a telephone interview. At least 48 people where
injured in the stampede, Kili said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Baudelaire Mieu in Abidjan at 
